{
  "stem": "23645.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because sometimes the Nazi-- the Gestapo men would walk in to see if there's anybody left in the barracks, before the other shift would come home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Do you understand what I'm saying?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So after a while, the fever broke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the doctor says, he's lucky, you know, that he's not dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were very anxious to get him back to become a human again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we started some nourishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then he-- when he felt strong enough, we thought he's going to go to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we wouldn't have to worry of him being discovered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What type of nourishment were you able to get for him?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The soup made out of potato peels-- there wasn't much, much value in that-- and of course, the bread that we were getting.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes you would find some potatoes in the soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a piece of bread that we would get, a piece of bread that was about inch in diameter and a bit of margarine, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most of the time, dry bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was-- can you imagine trying to get back to health, let alone sustain yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was a slow process.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was-- I had another source of getting some food, which I'll tell you in a short while how that was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what happened-- so that day, the first day, as he was standing there, you could see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because he was thin, because he had lost a lot of weight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't have any nourishment for some days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think it was 10 or 11 days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They picked him out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I knew one of the Gestapo men from work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had a very good relationship with him, because you know, he looked up to the kind of work I was doing.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
